  "title": "Sales Executive (Interior Design/ Commercial)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Generate leads and secure new business for commercial renovation and interior refurbishment projects.</li><li>Handle client inquiries related to office renovations, retail refurbishments, and commercial upgrades.</li><li>Coordinate with design, estimation, and project teams for renovation proposals and BOQs</li><li>Prepare and present cost estimates, proposals, and timelines.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Diploma and above</li><li>At least years of sales experience in <strong>commercial renovation / interior fit-out.</strong></li><li>Excellent communication, negotiation, and client-handling skills.</li><li>Target-driven with strong follow-up abilities.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
